features: Exceptional quality: only top-quality materials are used for the production of Japanese pull ups. Worry-free all night: even the baby with high body temperature and tends to be sweating a lot, this diaper pant can keep their bottom dry. body.description: INSPIRED Moony and Moony man products have superior gentile qualities that are designed to adapt to all stages of your precious child's growth. We will report on the inquisitive minds of the developers, and their wishes they placed in their product, for you and your baby. FEATURES: NEW TECHNOLOGY! Full-coverage high waist design! Breathable soft wavy top sheet does not stick to your baby's skin so your baby stays dry and comfortable. The airy soft gathers fit snugly in all positions.
